Modeling
May 21 2019

Vintage! I’m a total vintage girl. Seriously, flare jeans, weird tops, denim jackets. I see it, I want it. Sadly I ain’t got the budget for it! My friend Natalie owns a depop shop where she shops for vintage clothes and sells them. I don’t know about you but the joy of trying to find  vintage clothing is epic. Check out my girls Instagram and her shop for more looks!

We wanted something urban to show both a sweet side and and an edgy side. Nothing better than a downtown area of Ventura! Isaiah knows the best places to shoot at! 

We also were lucky to have Katelynn she is a miracle worker with this face!

I hope you like the looks we created together.

Natalie’s whole goal is to bring outfits together to show a persons personality. She is a stylist and can read people from the moment she meets them.
